<p>In terms of men checking me out, I&#8217;m generally not particularly bothered, but if someone screams &#8220;nice tits&#8221; out of a car window (and yes, this has happened to me &#8211; I was 12 at the time), it&#8217;s quite clearly objectification.  This is an entirely different situation from having dinner with a friend and noticing his eyes drifting down towards my chest.</p>
